OL,5,GThe BBC's reputation rests on its
OL,6,Gjournalism. The breakdowns during Laura
OL,7,GKuenssberg's interview with the Prime
OL,8,GMinister this morning will be taken
OL,9,Gseriously.
OL,11,FWhat went wrong? Could anything have
OL,12,Fbeen done differently? Or was it,
OL,13,Fsadly, just one of those things which
OL,14,Fhappen in live television?
OL,16,FThe fact the programme DOG remained
OL,17,Fthroughout the debacle suggests the
OL,18,Fprogramme was being routed to a gallery
OL,19,Fat New Broadcasting House.
OL,3,CWhere was BBC One Presentation during
OL,4,Cthis morning's technical problems?
