OL,5,FFrom here, it would have made its way
OL,6,Fto what we still like to think of as
OL,7,FNetwork Control aka Playout.
OL,9,FBut the public don't know or care
OL,10,Fwhether the mess they witnessed was the
OL,11,Fresponsibility of News or Presentation
OL,12,F they just care that a shambles went
OL,13,Fout on air.
OL,15,FIn the days when breakdowns were much
OL,16,Fmore frequent, Presentation protected
OL,17,Fthe BBC's integrity and sovereignty.
OL,18,FAfter a few seconds of black screen, up
OL,19,Fwould pop the programme slide or an
OL,20,Fapology caption.
