OL,5,FProblems can arise during any live
OL,6,Fprogramme but problems like these
OL,7,Fduring an interview with the PM are a
OL,8,Fconspiracy theorist's dream.
OL,10,FIf only the breakdown had been handled
OL,11,Fsmoothly by the announcer.
OL,13,FNo doubt behind the scenes, efforts
OL,14,Fwere being made to resolve the
OL,15,Fsituation and work out what to do.
OL,16,FThere is no question of a lack of
OL,17,Fprofessionalism.
